Racemod client UI + HUD data, vendored for the client-download pk3.

Upstream: https://github.com/DenMSC/racemod_data
Commit:   9aa3560a82cc4adcd7e8adb215f2fc205bfda40e (2024-04-02)

Contents: the "Racemod Options" gametype menu (ui/porkui/racemod_main.rml and
friends) plus the ale_racemod HUD and strafe-arrow assets. Packaged by the
server Dockerfile into racemod_ui_v6_local.pk3. The name deliberately does NOT
end in "pure" (clients only fetch explicit-pure paks from the dead official
mirror); instead the gametype pure-indexes the racemod_ui_v6.txt marker inside
it (GT_InitGametype in hrace.as), so with sv_pure 1 connecting clients download
it from this server automatically. Bump the marker + pak version (v6 -> v7,
here + hrace.as + Dockerfile + tv/Dockerfile + server.cfg) whenever the
contents change, or clients holding the old same-named pak fail the pure check.

Local additions (diverges from upstream):
  - ui/porkui/racemod_main.rml: "Race in reverse" / "Toggle triggers" command
    buttons + Binds rows, for the reverse race mode (see racemod/UPSTREAM).
